       <mj-text
       align="center"
       line-height="19px"
       font-size="15px"
       color="#545151">
       Earth Day is an annual event on April 22 to demonstrate support 
       for environmental protection. First held on April 22, 1970, it 
       now includes a wide range of events coordinated globally by 
       EarthDay.org including 1 billion people in more than 193 
       countries. The official theme for 2022 is Invest In Our Planet.
       </mj-text>


